{"tid":974794,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"紐約時報：中國健保系統崩潰　民衆被迫自己DIY癌症藥","createTime":"2019-01-09T07:04:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-09T15:40:50.000Z","uid":141151,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"d54d9576e4046209fd8b618835f34b898d56512c","tid":974794,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T07:04:35.000Z","msg":"紐約時報：中國健保系統崩潰　民衆被迫自己DIY癌症藥<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.taiwannews.com.tw/ch/news/3612608?fbclid=IwAR3Px6uzG988VtpO1IG0M-QoutMzAkw705-boCBXRNY6uITeSLmhzpLpPL8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.taiwannews.com.tw%2Fch%2Fnews%2F3612608%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3Px6uzG988VtpO1IG0M-QoutMzAkw705-boCBXRNY6uITeSLmhzpLpPL8&d=FTypIbPskK5BqgetbecOisn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=5f37f84d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.taiwannews.com.tw/ch/news/3612608?fbclid=IwAR3Px6uzG988VtpO1IG0M-QoutMzAkw705-boCBXRNY6uITeSLmhzpLpPL8</a><br />\n<br />\n(台灣英文新聞/吳東文 綜合外電報導)《紐約時報》發佈最新中國醫療紀錄片，指出該國的健保體制已崩潰。<br />\n<br />\n報導介紹，中國共産黨稱，現在中國健康保險，涵蓋了幾乎所有中國人，但該國的健保體系，其實早已崩潰。<br />\n<br />\n在文章内第一部影片中，《紐約時報》介紹一名中國男子，由於買不起母親的癌症藥，只好選擇去網路上購買配方並學習製作方法，「DIY癌症藥」，但男子使用的設備，明顯骯髒原始，效果令人質疑。<br />\n<br />\n在影片最後，《紐約時報》説明，受訪男子母親在採訪結束後已不幸過世。<br />\n<br />\n在第二部影片中，《紐約時報》介紹在中國大醫院旁，有所謂的「癌症街」，居住罹患癌症，卻無法負擔住院費用的鄉下民衆。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">報導引述世界衛生組織數據，表示每位醫生照顧民衆數，國際標準為1500到2000人，但在中國，一位醫師卻要負責治療6666位民衆。</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">China&rsquo;s Health Care Crisis</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/2019/01/07/world/asia/chinas-health-care-crisis.html?rref=collection\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2019%2F01%2F07%2Fworld%2Fasia%2Fchinas-health-care-crisis.html%3Frref%3Dcollection&d=FTypIbPskK5BqgetbecOisn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=e823cb46\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nytimes.com/2019/01/07/world/asia/chinas-health-care-crisis.html?rref=collection</a>"},{"pid":"af885c6e8341482e3dff829a97aa3ea9c21a28d3","tid":974794,"uid":45914,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T07:05:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9889d0a014e57b51018f81ea262d766bfd82399b","tid":974794,"uid":47042,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T07:16:03.000Z","msg":"skr<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dca561a6244a88bd3de9997dff867afa8ba5164f","tid":974794,"uid":29080,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T07:32:29.000Z","msg":"全民煉丹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72bc3eec4f95c692b05c66b8735719010609d65d","tid":974794,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T14:23:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d372b168c6f0a2cf6772a3a2fc4c7bc38ff1bdd2","tid":974794,"uid":220701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T14:25:03.000Z","msg":"666？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b60365f9aac096eaf0f3c8861f7dfddc412b5f18","tid":974794,"uid":511,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T14:25:10.000Z","msg":"自煮燃發<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c6bc5abb9f126e9eabc96d7afdb13999d89728d","tid":974794,"uid":59695,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"